title: The iPad Book Volume 6 - 2014  UK
description:
The iPad Book Volume 6 - 2014  UK

180 Pages | True PDF | English | 16 MB 

Whether you own an iPad, iPad Air or iPad mini, the new volume of The iPad Book is the perfect companion. It will guide you through all of the in-built apps, exploring the most basic functions and the more advanced features in easy-to-follow tutorials. We even have a complete guide to iOS 8, Apple's latest operating system. Featuring: Guide to iOS 8 - Discover everything you need to know about Apple's latest operating system. Get creative - Apply photo edits, make your own movies and create incredible music. Be productive - Make your professional and personal lives easier by getting on top of things using your iPad's apps. The essential apps - Discover the best third-party apps available from the App Store.
